query:
/*+  */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 10 AND q1.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('ell',
'rpg',
'sharepoint',
'travel',
'webmasters')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('articles',
'difference',
'document-library',
'domains',
'jquery',
'paperwork',
'past-tense',
'permissions',
'redirects',
'sentence-structure',
'sharepoint-addin',
'transit',
'verbs',
'visa-refusals',
'wordpress')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.question_id = q1.id
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.upvotes >= 0 AND u1.upvotes <= 100 group by t1.name;
